<HEADLINE> French Senator Says 21st Century Will Not Be American </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, May 2 (Xinhua) -- Pierre Biarnes, a French Senator from
the Socialist Party and former Africa correspondent for the daily Le
Monde, said in his newest book that the 21st century will not be
dominated by the United States.
</P>
<P>
In the book entitled "The 21st Century Will Not Be American,"
Biarnes said that the coming century will be multipolar and
multicultural as the world used to be in the past centuries.
</P>
<P>
