the world's population, is not destined to always dictate to the
whole planet," he said.
</P>
<P>
He said that the two extremes of the immense Euro-Asia
continent are "raising forces that will jeopardize the American
hegemony, which is nothing but ephemeral."
</P>
<P>
"Seven years after the Gulf War, America had to renounce using
again its brutal force against Iraq. This time, all those who
said no sent calmly but firmly a message to it -- Enough!" he
said. 
</P>
