information on the List Voting System which will be used for the
geographical constituency election in the coming Legislative
Council (LegCo) Election by calling a hotline 187-8877 starting
from Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The new interactive phone system speaks three languages --
Chinese (Putonghua), Cantonese and English, and will carry on
until the election day on May 24.
</P>
